{"tid":1127411,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"海日灣II買家王太：樓價一直無跌過","createTime":"2019-04-27T05:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T02:21:47.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"04dc3309af6b79ab3298bbcd7a1c91a2f2e9f0f1","tid":1127411,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:58:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20190427/s00011/a463c76bc847b14401b9f910e44056dd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20190427%2Fs00011%2Fa463c76bc847b14401b9f910e44056dd.png&h=484dae89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現居於土瓜灣的王生及王太，剛斥資約840萬元購入海日灣II 2房戶。王太表示，現時租住土瓜灣面積較細的2房戶，「樓價一路無跌過，與其租樓交租，不如買樓。」<br />\n<br />\n她透露，過去有參觀將軍澳二手樓，但價錢跟全新樓差不多，所以購入一手樓可慳裝修家電等駛費。而王生過去亦曾居於大埔區，認為白石角有升值潛力，故購入海日灣II的單位自用。<br />\n<br />\n對於發展商以價單形式推售，她直言，這個做法清𥇦明確，在財務上有充足準備；反之，招標要依靠代理提示入標，不太清晰，所以當初沒有以此途徑購買一手樓。"},{"pid":"0a8bdf0fedf315335558f8384e0a04a1fdf140ae","tid":1127411,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:59:40.000Z","msg":"專家食屎<br />\n連登仔等瞓街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d353b3718121b0f052e03c98ad9798c8b84e82","tid":1127411,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:59:48.000Z","msg":"叫淡淡點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65883c41934fbe377a3e72eac389fcd47a5ea13","tid":1127411,"uid":104965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:00:41.000Z","msg":"我真係恭喜你呀！<br />\n快撚D供完佢呀"},{"pid":"5007a535881dea3668565c73fa34dcf91ddcba13","tid":1127411,"uid":47135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:03:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓市go go  go<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082362e997b297dbf1da155fe5d3e7c1a1d47cd1"